  description="How disc stack centrifuge capacity is determined: swallowing vs rated vs real-world throughput, and the effect of viscosity, temperature, and particle size on throughput."
  heroImage="/images/disc-stack-centrifuge-capacity/Disc-Stack-Centrifuge-Capacity-Factors-600.webp"
  heroImageAlt="Disc stack centrifuge capacity factors diagram"
